
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as Admin
    participant FE as Admin Login<br/>Next.js :3001
    participant BE as Backend<br/>Express API
    participant AUTH as Auth<br/>Middleware
    participant DB as Database<br/>PostgreSQL

    Admin ->> FE: Buka /admin/login
    activate FE
    FE -->> Admin: Tampil form Username + Password
    deactivate FE

    Admin ->> FE: Input username dan password
    Admin ->> FE: Klik Login
    activate FE
    FE ->> BE: POST /api/admin/login
    activate BE
    BE ->> AUTH: validateCredentials (username, password)
    activate AUTH
    AUTH ->> AUTH: bcrypt.compare (password, hash)

    alt Kredensial salah
        AUTH -->> BE: invalid credentials
        BE -->> FE: 401 Unauthorized
        FE -->> Admin: Error - username atau password salah
    else Kredensial benar
        AUTH ->> AUTH: jwt.sign (role=admin, JWT_SECRET)
        AUTH -->> BE: token, expiresIn
        BE -->> FE: 200 OK - token
        FE ->> FE: Simpan token di session/cookie
        FE -->> Admin: Redirect ke /admin dashboard
    end

    deactivate AUTH
    deactivate BE
    deactivate FE

    Note over Admin, DB: Setiap request admin berikutnya

    Admin ->> FE: Akses halaman admin
    activate FE
    FE ->> BE: Request + Authorization Bearer token
    activate BE
    BE ->> AUTH: verifyToken (token)
    activate AUTH

    alt Token expired atau invalid
        AUTH -->> BE: 403 Forbidden
        BE -->> FE: 403
        FE -->> Admin: Redirect ke /admin/login
    else Token valid
        AUTH -->> BE: decoded payload OK
        BE -->> FE: Data response
        FE -->> Admin: Tampil konten halaman
    end

    deactivate AUTH
    deactivate BE
    deactivate FE